@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_znvoie(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp(((v1 + 0.65 * v2 + 0.08) * v0))
    v0 = tmp
    v2 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.58 * v0 + 0.38)) + v2)
    v1 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.37 - tmp + 0.09)) * (0.26 / v2))
    data[tid] = v0
